title: Jodanukar
text: Jodanukar (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Jodānūkar; also known as Jodānokar) is a village in <a href="Divshal%20Rural%20District">Divshal Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Langarud%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Langarud%20County">Langarud County</a>, <a href="Gilan%20Province">Gilan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 304, in 91 families.
